Package: c3r
Type: Package
Title: An htmlwidgets interface to the c3.js d3 charting library
Version: 0.1
Date: 2015-02-21
Author: Harlan Harris (@harlanh)
Maintainer: Harlan Harris <harlan@harris.name>
Description: c3.js is a D3-based charting libary and this package
    provides an htmlwidgets interface to it.
URL: http://github.com/harlanh/c3r
BugReports: https://github.com/harlanh/c3r/issues
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Suggests:
    testthat
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0),
    htmlwidgets,
    htmltools
Imports:
    magrittr
